以上10年以下有期徒刑，得併科2百萬元以下罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/111%2c%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c1763%2c20221025%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,111,交簡,1763,20221025,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"交簡","JNO":"1763","JDATE":"20221025","JTITLE":"公共危險"}